    <title>Known issues and other information</title>

<para>
 <emphasis role="strong">Known Issues with Java 9</emphasis>
</para>
<itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        Starting AUTs will not work without <emphasis>--permit-illegal-acces</emphasis>
        set for the java virtual machine. Sometimes also 
        <emphasis>--add-modules=ALL-SYSTEM</emphasis> is necessary.
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        JavaFx testing ComboBox, Slider, TableView and TreeTableViews will not work.
    </para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>

</section>
